    • Seed

      public Seed(String name, String type, int harvestTime, int waterNeed, int fertilizerNeed, int cost, int basePrice, double xp)
      Constructs the seed with the given name, type, harvest time, number of water and fertilizer needs, cost, base price, and experience
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the seed
      type - the type of the seed
      harvestTime - the number of days it needs to grow
      waterNeed - the number of times it needs to be watered
      fertilizerNeed - the number of times it needs to be fertilized
      cost - the cost of the seed
      basePrice - the base selling price of the seed
      xp - the experience gained after harvesting the seed
